you opening of the borders.

01:06:45.510 --> 01:06:47.790
Ask them after the
refugee crisis,

01:06:47.790 --> 01:06:50.210
what is the things
that you fear most?

01:06:50.210 --> 01:06:52.500
Opening of the borders.

01:06:52.500 --> 01:06:55.460
And from this point of view
the fact where the best

01:06:55.460 --> 01:06:57.670
and the worst happened
to be the same.

01:06:57.670 --> 01:07:02.200
Is a kind of miss in the
important political reality

01:07:02.200 --> 01:07:05.430
that we are talking about,
but I am going to stop here.

