01:08:04.150 --> 01:08:05.470
&gt;&gt; John Van Houdt: Thank you

01:08:05.470 --> 01:08:10.660
for those presentations,
very interesting.

01:08:10.660 --> 01:08:13.200
My name is John Van Houdt
and I'm from The Library

01:08:13.200 --> 01:08:14.630
of Congress, I worked

01:08:14.630 --> 01:08:17.430
on European politics
for a long time.

